  "description": "<p>A quirk is similar to a compulsion in that it is an odd behavior that is repeated often, but quirks are usually subtler behavior and lack the urgency that compulsions have on a character. People with a quirk may not even notice that they have the quirk as it’s just part of their normal behavior. However, a quirk that comes about from corruption may come across to others more troubling than purely odd.</p>",
